## English landing-page strings for Contract Studio.
##
## Source of truth for marketing copy. Keep msgstrs identical to msgids
## here — Gettext fallback uses msgid when msgstr is empty, but having
## them written out makes localisation diffs cleaner.
##
## When adding a string, register it on the page first via gettext("…"),
## then run `mix gettext.extract --merge` to push it into landing.pot
## and merge into landing.po (en/ + ko/).
